= Biography 

Zhi Zhou received the B.Eng. and M.Eng degrees from the Scholl of Computer Science & Technology, Huazhong University of Science & Technology (HUST), in 2012 and 2014, respectively. 
He also minored in finance from 2008 to 2012, in Wuhan University. He is currently working toward the Ph.D. degree in the School of Computer Science and Technology, HUST, under the 
supervision of Prof. Fangming Liu. His primary research interests include green cloud computing, smart grid, and network support for wide-area data analytics.
